because that's what life would be like.

28:38.649 --> 28:41.484
And yet, you're about to
get remarried to your husband.

28:45.957 --> 28:49.292
Good night.
I'll be in the living room.

29:50.688 --> 29:52.021
Oh, no.

29:53.157 --> 29:54.924
