the opportunity to sleep with but didn't.

31:00.324 --> 31:01.791
Was it Adrian?

31:03.027 --> 31:04.594
Was it Adrian? Was it?

31:04.628 --> 31:06.930
What the... Adrian?

31:06.964 --> 31:09.799
