That's what you think...

32:21.171 --> 32:22.639
that she's not
good enough for him

32:22.673 --> 32:24.574
because he's such a nice guy,

32:24.608 --> 32:27.110
and he would never get involved
with a girl like Adrian.

32:27.144 --> 32:30.013
I did not say that.
She's a nice girl... Adrian.

32:30.047 --> 32:32.815
I know.
No, you don't know.

32:32.850 --> 32:35.818
You're being nice to her,
but be honest here.

32:35.853 --> 32:37.820
You think it was lousy
of her to seduce Ben,

32:37.855 --> 32:41.190
