33:11.689 --> 33:13.523
Are you planning
to use this time

33:13.557 --> 33:16.392
while Ben's with Adrian
as some experiment?

33:16.427 --> 33:19.696
You know, a time to find out if
we're really meant for each other

33:19.730 --> 33:21.698
so that if we're not,

33:21.732 --> 33:23.366
when Ben and Adrian's
baby gets here

33:23.400 --> 33:25.234
and all hell breaks loose
a couple months into it,

33:25.269 --> 33:27.070
