you'd rather be with him?

33:27.104 --> 33:30.540
No! This has nothing to do with
them... with Ben and Adrian.

33:30.574 --> 33:33.843
This is about us.

33:33.877 --> 33:35.144
I want this summer

33:35.179 --> 33:37.246
to be our time to get
to know each other

33:37.281 --> 33:40.583
and to see if there's any chance
we can actually be a couple

33:40.618 --> 33:43.319
and actually get married
in the distant future

33:43.354 --> 33:46.255
and be a family...
the three of us.

33:46.290 --> 33:48.324
I have a difficult
time believing

33:48.359 --> 33:51.394
that whatever our feelings are
for Ben and Adrian...

33:51.428 --> 33:53.596
that those feelings
don't have something to do

33:53.631 --> 33:56.799
with everything going on
with us right now.

33:56.834 --> 33:59.435
And I also have
a difficult time believing

33:59.470 --> 34:02.105
that going to movies
and going out to dinner

34:02.139 --> 34:04.240
and taking John to the circus

34:04.274 --> 34:06.643
would help us decide what our
feelings are for each other

34:06.677 --> 34:09.277
and whether or not we wanna be
together the rest of our lives.

34:09.313 --> 34:11.313
But that's what
people do, okay?

34:11.348 --> 34:14.183
They go out. They talk.
They get to know each other.

34:14.217 --> 34:15.885
They... they fall in love,

34:15.918 --> 34:18.286
and then they get married...
Sometimes.

34:20.290 --> 34:23.059
I want that.

34:23.092 --> 34:26.295
And while we're going out
and talking

34:26.330 --> 34:28.297
and getting to know each other

34:28.331 --> 34:30.967
and falling in love,

34:33.670 --> 34:36.005
I wanna graduate high school,

34:36.040 --> 34:39.842
and I wanna graduate college
and start a career.

34:41.210 --> 34:43.212
I wanna be a teacher.

34:43.246 --> 34:45.782
I wanna teach girls
to believe in themselves,

34:45.815 --> 34:48.051
because I believe in myself.

34:50.120 --> 34:52.655
I believe I can be
a good teacher

34:52.690 --> 34:55.858
and a good mother

34:55.893 --> 34:58.661
and a good wife to you,
someday.

35:23.378 --> 35:26.146
Grace, your phone's beeping.

35:26.181 --> 35:28.182
