She trusts us.

36:06.521 --> 36:09.123
She trusts me anyway.

36:10.125 --> 36:12.293
See you later.
I'll call you.

36:12.327 --> 36:15.496
Tell your mom I said hello.
I'm really looking forward to meeting her.

36:15.530 --> 36:17.398
I'll introduce you.

36:17.432 --> 36:20.200
She's a very special person...
my mom...

36:20.235 --> 36:23.937
