38:13.331 --> 38:16.633
No, most of the time
you are perfect.

38:16.668 --> 38:18.168
Too perfect for me.

38:18.203 --> 38:21.805
Adrian, I am not too perfect,

38:21.840 --> 38:23.941
especially for you.

38:23.975 --> 38:26.844
In fact, I don't even know
