38:26.878 --> 38:28.779
What are you talking about?

38:28.813 --> 38:30.881
You're just so...

38:30.915 --> 38:34.284
Full of life and...Fun

38:34.319 --> 38:36.820
and crazy and carefree

38:36.855 --> 38:39.389
and...Beautiful,

38:39.424 --> 38:41.325
and I'm not.

38:41.359 --> 38:43.894
But you're very confident

38:43.928 --> 38:47.898
and considerate and...Just
such an honorable person.

38:47.932 --> 38:51.902
You have dignity...
real dignity, Ben.

38:51.936 --> 38:54.004
Oh, at least
when your hair is combed.

38:55.473 --> 38:57.973
I really appreciate
you standing by me like this,

38:58.626 --> 39:01.028
and I hope you continue
to do that...

39:01.062 --> 39:03.964
to stand by me even when Amy
comes back from New York.

39:03.998 --> 39:07.100
And I think it's really nice
that she called me

39:07.135 --> 39:09.369
and that she's offering
to be my friend,

39:09.404 --> 39:11.205
