40:52.557 --> 40:54.458
and being with John.

40:54.492 --> 40:56.393
You're welcome.

40:57.996 --> 40:59.430
I'll call you later.

40:59.464 --> 41:01.632
Great. I'll look forward
to hearing from you.

41:01.666 --> 41:04.602
